    APIGateway -->|Classify 'SQL' or 'RAG'| QueryClassifier;
    QueryClassifier --> RequestRouter;

    RequestRouter -- If SQL --> SQLQueryGen;
    SQLQueryGen -->|Run Query| SQLDatabase;
